    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. While the engine runs consistently and the car remains roadworthy, potential buyers should expect some minor cosmetic wear and tear, as well as typical mechanical signs of age such as small fluid seeps. It is a solid choice for those who need a functional vehicle and are comfortable with a few minor imperfections.",
